    • Field Detail

      • windowSize

        protected int windowSize
        Streaming messages are only kept until the window size is met. by default the window size is 1, so all messages are forwarded as they arrive.

      • localWindowCount

        protected int localWindowCount
        variable used to keep track of the current local window count. This value is always reset to 0 after it reaches the windowSize
